queries.sql: SELECT tc.CONSTRAINT_NAME, tc.TABLE_NAME, kcu.COLUMN_NAME, rc.REFERENCED_TABLE_NAME, kcu.REFERENCED_COLUMN_NAME FROM information_schema.TABLE_CONSTRAINTS AS tc INNER JOIN information_schema.REFERENTIAL_CONSTRAINTS AS rc ON tc.CONSTRAINT_NAME = rc.CONSTRAINT_NAME INNER JOIN information_schema.KEY_COLUMN_USAGE AS kcu ON tc.CONSTRAINT_NAME = kcu.CONSTRAINT_NAME WHERE tc.CONSTRAINT_TYPE = 'FOREIGN KEY' AND tc.TABLE_SCHEMA = 'exemples' AND tc.TABLE_NAME = 'escritorios'
